                            automatic bike rental system
                            ============================


SUPPORTED OPERATING SYSTEMS :
-----------------------------

The automatic bike rental system works on :

 - Windows 8/10
 

REQUIREMENTS :
-------------

 - WampServer
 - Postgresql
 - Composer
 - tortoisesvn

BUILDING AND INSTALLING  :
_________________________
 - Install WampServer
Download and install WampServer via this URL :  http://www.wampserver.com/

 - Install PostgreSQL
Follow those instructions : http://www.mickaelsylvestre.com/2013/07/installer-postgresql-avec-wamp/  in order to install PostgreSQL and PhpPgAdmin with WampServer

 - Install Composer
Download and install Composer via this URL : https://getcomposer.org/download/

 - Laravel installation
 You need to enable those extensions : 
   OpenSSL PHP Extension  
   PDO PHP Extension
   Mbstring PHP Extension
   Tokenizer PHP Extension
This video will show you how to enable those extensions with WampServer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R2olTlKZmMU 

 - Download tortoise svn
Visit this website, download and install tortoise svn : https://tortoisesvn.net/downloads.html

 - Download our project 
Checkout our project in the www  WampServer directory
Visit this website to see how to checkout a project : https://tortoisesvn.net/docs/nightly/TortoiseSVN_en/tsvn-dug-checkout.html
The URL of our project is : https://services.emi.u-bordeaux.fr/projet/svn/pdp-pret-de-velo

Our project is divide in two : 
  - Admin part : you can access the admin part via : http://localhost/pdp-pret-de-velo/website/pdp-admin/pdp/public/panel/login
  - Client part : you can access the client part via : http://localhost/pdp-pret-de-velo/website/pdp/public/

Then go in the www/pdp-pret-de-velo/website/pdp folder and type this line in a terminal : 

 - php artisan migrate 
The client part is now available.

Then go in the www/pdp-pret-de-velo/pdp-admin/pdp folder and type those lines in a terminal:

 - php artisan panel:install
 - php artisan panel:crud users
 - php artisan panel:crud Bike
The admin part is now available



